title: Clinton In Only Candidate On Stage To Vote For Iraq War (Republican Party)
text: ( Source : Republican Party ) On October 11 , 2002 , Clinton Voted In Favor Of A Joint Resolution To Authorize The Use Of Military Force Against Iraq . ( H.J. Res 114 , Roll Call Vote #237: Passed 77-23: R 48-1; D 29-22, 10/11/02, Clinton Voted
